Slide 5 — Market insight + opportunity
The keyboard market optimized for novelty instead of outcomes

Expression keyboards assume:

Customization drives retention.

But user behavior shows the opposite.

When typing becomes unreliable or intrusive, users switch back to native keyboards like Gboard.

Three common assumptions:

Customization drives engagement

Users actually prioritize speed and reliability.

Ads sustain the free model

Heavy ads disrupt messaging.

Emoji novelty drives growth

Users want faster communication decisions, not more emoji packs.

Opportunity

AI that helps users:

react instantly
respond quickly
express tone naturally

Without interrupting typing.

