Slide 8 — Technical implementation
High-level AI architecture

Facemoji AI can be implemented through a layered architecture.

Context layer

conversation text
recent messages
language detection
user preferences

AI understanding layer

LLM-powered intent classification

detects:

reaction intent
reply intent
translation needs
content generation requests

Agent layer

multiple specialized agents:

Reaction agent

emoji and GIF recommendations

Conversation agent

summaries and smart replies

Creation agent

captions, meme text, emoji combos

Action agent

search and planning tasks

Model stack

LLM for generation and summarization
multimodal models for images and stickers
ranking models for emoji suggestions

Delivery layer

suggestion chips
emoji strip
quick reply buttons
action cards

AI assistance remains optional, fast, and non-intrusive to preserve typing performance.

